<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 00:56:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>干预风险迫在眉睫，美元逼近 160 日元关键水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-flirts-with-key-160-yen-level-intervention-risk-looms-2024-06-25/</link><description>周二，遭受重创的日元在 1 美元兑 160 美元附近徘徊，交易员对日本当局为支撑日元而采取的任何干预措施保持高度警惕，而美元在大盘中小幅走高。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 00:52:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-flirts-with-key-160-yen-level-intervention-risk-looms-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>市场权衡供应紧张和中国经济复苏，油价稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-steady-markets-weigh-supply-tensions-china-economic-recovery-2024-06-25/</link><description>周二油价几乎没有变化，因为对中国经济复苏前景的担忧抵消了中东紧张局势和乌克兰袭击俄罗斯炼油厂引发的供应担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 00:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-steady-markets-weigh-supply-tensions-china-economic-recovery-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国调查中国电信、中国移动互联网、云风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-probing-china-telecom-china-mobile-over-internet-cloud-risks-2024-06-25/</link><description>三名知情人士称，拜登政府正在调查中国移动、中国电信和中国联通，因为担心这些公司可能通过其美国云和互联网业务向北京提供美国数据。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 00:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-probing-china-telecom-china-mobile-over-internet-cloud-risks-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>普华永道表示，随着员工拥抱人工智能、提高技能，“伟大的辞职”进入第三个年头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/great-resignation-enters-third-year-workers-embrace-ai-upskilling-pwc-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>普华永道对全球劳动力的一项调查发现，预计在未来 12 个月内更换雇主的工人比例高于 2022 年“大辞职”时期的比例。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 23:07:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/great-resignation-enters-third-year-workers-embrace-ai-upskilling-pwc-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>年中购物节失败后中国零售前景黯淡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-retail-outlook-dims-after-mid-year-shopping-festival-flop-2024-06-24/</link><description>在经历了令人失望的年中网上购物节之后，中国零售商面临着令人畏惧的近期未来，这也给世界第二大经济体的复苏前景蒙上了阴影。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 23:03:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-retail-outlook-dims-after-mid-year-shopping-festival-flop-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国驳回加拿大对新疆人权问题的投诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dismisses-canadian-complaints-over-xinjiang-human-rights-2024-06-24/</link><description>中国周一驳回了加拿大关于渥太华所说的关于西部新疆地区侵犯人权行为的“可信报告”的投诉，并表示渥太华应该关注自己的歧视问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 20:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dismisses-canadian-complaints-over-xinjiang-human-rights-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国外交官称，美国需要中国人文学科学生和印度科学学生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-needs-chinese-students-humanities-indian-students-sciences-us-diplomat-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>这位排名第二的美国外交官周一表示，美国应该欢迎更多来自中国的学生，但应该学习人文学科而不是科学，并指出出于安全考虑，美国大学正在限制中国学生接触敏感技术。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 18:15:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-needs-chinese-students-humanities-indian-students-sciences-us-diplomat-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>白宫官员表示，微软与 G42 的协议是积极的，因为它切断了与华为的联系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-g42-deal-positive-because-it-cut-huawei-ties-white-house-official-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>一位白宫官员周一表示，微软向人工智能公司 G42 投资 15 亿美元的交易“总体上是一个积极的进展”，因为它迫使这家总部位于阿拉伯联合酋长国的公司断绝了与中国华为的关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 16:39:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-g42-deal-positive-because-it-cut-huawei-ties-white-house-official-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>印度 Amara Raja 与中国国轩签署锂离子电池制造许可协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-amara-raja-inks-licensing-deal-with-chinas-gotion-lithium-ion-cell-2024-06-24/</link><description>印度电池制造商Amara Raja Energy and Mobility周一表示，该公司与中国国轩高科技公司旗下子公司Gotion-InoBat-Batteries (GIB)签署了一项许可协议，在印度生产锂离子电池。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 15:53:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-amara-raja-inks-licensing-deal-with-chinas-gotion-lithium-ion-cell-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大受欧盟和美国启发考虑对中国电动汽车征收进口关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/canada-says-it-might-impose-import-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-06-24/</link><description>加拿大周一表示，正在考虑是否对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税，因为它寻求与盟友结盟，反对他们认为受到大量补贴的中国产业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 15:22:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/canada-says-it-might-impose-import-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国男子袭击校车致三人受伤，其中包括日本妇女和儿童</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/man-attacks-school-bus-china-wounding-japanese-woman-child-nhk-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>日本驻上海总领事馆的一名官员表示，周一，一名男子手持疑似刀子袭击了中国苏州一所日本学校使用的一辆公交车，严重伤害了一名中国妇女，并打伤了一名日本妇女和她的孩子。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:45:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/man-attacks-school-bus-china-wounding-japanese-woman-child-nhk-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>波兰总统表示希望中国帮助乌克兰实现和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/polish-president-says-he-hopes-china-can-help-bring-peace-ukraine-2024-06-24/</link><description>波兰总统安杰伊·杜达周一在访问北京期间表示，他希望中国帮助找到尊重国际法的乌克兰和平解决方案。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:37:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/polish-president-says-he-hopes-china-can-help-bring-peace-ukraine-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国赣锋锂矿公司就墨西哥锂矿提请仲裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/miners-including-chinas-ganfeng-launch-arbitration-case-against-mexico-over-2024-06-24/</link><description>据世界银行争端解决中心称，中国赣锋锂业及其两家打算在墨西哥开发锂项目的子公司就采矿特许权向墨西哥政府提起仲裁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:27:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/miners-including-chinas-ganfeng-launch-arbitration-case-against-mexico-over-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国称俄罗斯可能正在讨论帮助朝鲜发展导弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-russia-could-be-discussing-help-north-korea-missile-development-2024-06-24/</link><description>美国副国务卿库尔特·坎贝尔周一表示，俄罗斯和朝鲜之间关于平壤向莫斯科提供武器的回报的讨论可能与朝鲜的核远程导弹开发有关。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 14:11:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-russia-could-be-discussing-help-north-korea-missile-development-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警称在争议岛屿附近“驱离”日本船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coastguard-says-it-drove-away-japanese-boats-near-disputed-islands-2024-06-24/</link><description>中国海警周一表示，已对6月20日至24日期间进入钓鱼岛“领海”的四艘日本渔船和几艘巡逻艇采取了“必要管控措施”并“驱离”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 12:44:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coastguard-says-it-drove-away-japanese-boats-near-disputed-islands-2024-06-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>